# - Try to find libmagic 5.07
# Once done this will define
#
#  MAGIC_FOUND - system has libmagic
#  MAGIC_INCLUDE_DIRS - the libmagic include directory
#  MAGIC_LIBRARIES - Link these to use libmagic
